{"tid":1067434,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"相遇相知相愛 真係好幸運","createTime":"2019-03-18T13:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T18:43:37.000Z","uid":191552,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a598cfa7a24a34fcefb16929186f7ffd4308fe21","tid":1067434,"uid":191552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"突然係到諗<br />\n兩個人能夠係人海中相遇 再相知同相愛真係一件好幸運嘅事<br />\n要遇到對方已經唔係一件容易嘅事<br />\n然後要大家都對對方有好感有興趣<br />\n大家都係對方心目中想搵到嘅人<br />\n有晒天時地利人和先有機會係埋一齊<br />\n有時都係到諗 究竟係要有幾幸運先可以擁有身邊嘅另一半<br />\n所以大家要珍惜依家拖住個個佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adbb5b4518a0a27e38a2df0b4734d5bbbcc19bf","tid":1067434,"uid":197743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"今日行行下返屋企都突然諗起 相遇相知相愛呢句 諗起同前度由相識開始到分手嘅回憶 有另一半嘅真係好好珍惜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c85411218bc554ec63b8d185db59b703cfdec5","tid":1067434,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T18:43:37.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />🥳"}]}